{"word":"διαφορέω","slug":"διαφορέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διαφορέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:διαφέρω'><el>διαφέρω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to spread abroad</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to carry away, carry off</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <a href='S:especially'>esp.</a> as plunder, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to plunder</i>, <el>οἶκον, πόλιν</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>διαφορεῖσθαι ὑπό τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>4. </b><i>to tear in pieces</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to carry across from one place to another</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}